column2: #portfolioday. My name is Dani and I'm a visual artist from Brazil. My work mainly comes from the technique of free drawing. The #Brazilian culture had a strong influence on my weird drawings and chaotic paintings
column3: and it's also heavily inspired by South American aesthetics. https://t.co/eUWgdrQDuY
